200	 * - `'user'`: If the user is authenticated but does not have an admin role.
201	 * - `'admin'`: If the user is authenticated and has an admin role.
202	 *
203	 * The function uses `auth.api` to fetch the current session and determines
204	 * the user's role based on the session data.
